data.description: Spectacular Glendale 2 bedroom and loft condo centrally located, just minutes from Cherry Creek, Downtown Denver and DTC. You will enter through a park like setting of greenbelt, up an open staircase to the second-floor porch area and front door. The homes main floor consists of an open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dining area, 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and family room with an open stairway to the loft area. Ther is also stairway access in the back of the home which leads directly to your detached garage.
